org.deidentifier.arx.io

Class ImportAdapterCSV

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deidentifier.arx.io.ImportAdapter
      • org.deidentifier.arx.io.ImportAdapterCSV
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<java.lang.String[]>

    public class ImportAdapterCSV
extends ImportAdapter
    Import adapter for CSV files This adapter can import data from a CSV file. The CSV file itself is described by an appropriate ImportConfigurationCSV object. Internally this class makes use of CSVDataInput to read the CSV file on a line by line basis. A counting input stream (@link CountingInputStream} is used in order for {@link #getProgress() to be able to return the percentage of data that has already been processed.
